"{\"uid\": \"dailypost.ng-2024-08-03-paris-2024-olympics-im-not-happy-thierry-henry-fumes-after-france-beat-argentina\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Published  on  By  France U-23 coach, Thierry Henry, was not happy despite their 1-0 win over Argentina in their Olympics football match on Friday night.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 153, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19, \"end\": 25, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999940883, \"rank\": 5.892763895161306e-12, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 38, \"end\": 51, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thierry_Henry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thierry Henry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thierry_Henry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thierry_Henry\"}, {\"begin\": 94, \"end\": 103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999619629831294, \"rank\": 3.802403884577656e-05, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was high tension after the game as both sets of players clashed.\", \"from\": 155, \"to\": 225, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jean-Philippe Mateta's bullet header in the sixth minute proved to be the winning goal.\", \"from\": 227, \"to\": 314, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 227, \"end\": 247, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Philippe_Mateta\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jean-Philippe Mateta\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Philippe_Mateta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Philippe_Mateta\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Henry's men have now qualified for the semi-finals where they will face Egypt.\", \"from\": 316, \"to\": 394, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 388, \"end\": 393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.999999999863121, \"rank\": 1.3627882776197486e-10, \"text\": \"Egypt\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was tension ahead of the game after members of Argentina's triumphant Copa America squad were filmed singing a racist and transphobic chant aimed toward the French.\", \"from\": 396, \"to\": 566, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 449, \"end\": 458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999619629831294, \"rank\": 3.802403884577656e-05, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 559, \"end\": 565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9938577301733907, \"rank\": 0.005951796960943808, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chelsea midfielder, Enzo Fernandez, livestreamed the video on Instagram, with his club team-mate and France defender Wesley Fofana describing it as \\\"uninhibited racism\\\".\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 737, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 568, \"end\": 575, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999999999151896, \"rank\": 8.471887439400846e-11, \"text\": \"Chelsea\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 630, \"end\": 639, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.079419864133043e-17, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}, {\"begin\": 669, \"end\": 675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999940883, \"rank\": 5.892763895161306e-12, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 685, \"end\": 698, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wesley_Fofana_(rugby_union)\", \"score\": 0.6086950943009731, \"rank\": 0.6428571428571876, \"text\": \"Wesley Fofana\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wesley_Fofana_(rugby_union)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wesley_Fofana_(rugby_union)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"French supporters booed and jeered Argentina's squad at the Nouveau Stade de Bordeaux before and during the match.\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 853, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 739, \"end\": 745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9938577301733907, \"rank\": 0.005951796960943808, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 774, \"end\": 783, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999619629831294, \"rank\": 3.802403884577656e-05, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it all culminated in the ugly clash at full time, resulting in Enzo Millot being shown a red card.\", \"from\": 855, \"to\": 957, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 922, \"end\": 933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enzo_Millot\", \"score\": 0.9999983397394911, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Enzo Millot\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enzo_Millot\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enzo_Millot\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking afterwards, Henry said: \\\"I do not agree with what happened at the end of the match.\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 1051, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My player [Millot] got a red card and I do not accept it, it should not happen.\", \"from\": 1052, \"to\": 1131, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I could not control what happened.\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1168, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I went to greet the coach and when I turned around, what happened happened.\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1244, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We won, but I did not like what happened at the end with my player.\\\"\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1315, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympics 2024: Sports Minister updates on Favour Ofili's 100m race exclusion, raises posers  Transfer: Maresca breaks silence after banning Chelsea player from dressing room  UCL: 'That's not victory' - Thierry Henry on what Bar\\u00e7a did to Newcastle  EPL: A lot of people do not want Arsenal to win title - Thierry Henry  EPL: Thierry Henry gives Man Utd captain, Bruno Fernandes new nickname  'Can we be fair' - Thierry Henry defends Mbappe  UCL: Thierry Henry names two clubs to win trophy this season  UCL: 'Victor how body dey' - Thierry Henry speaks pidgin